profile:
At WATERMAN, 95% of our business is referral. Most of our work comes directly from contractors. Cut out the middle man by calling us today to receive contractor rates.  
 
There are a lot of things we could tell you about ourselves, and how we became the best company to call when you’re dealing with a drain back up in Toronto. We can begin by telling you that we began as a plumber to other plumbers – stepping in to subcontract on projects when other professionals ran into a drain back up in that they couldn’t handle on their own. The dozens of plumbing companies we work with have been so impressed with us, that they have used us again and again as the experts for repairs to drains, flooded basements, and even sewer back ups.
 
Roto-rooter, camera inspection of drainage system. Thermal image inspection of foundation leaks. Drain flushing. Pipe burst. Torpedo services. Foundations. Waterproofing. Plumbing repairs and installations. Basement Lowering, Sewer Backup, 24 hour emergency service
 
But of course, it’s hard to keep a service like ours secret for very long. We quickly started to gain a reputation as the business to deal with for a drain back up in Toronto.

profile: Since 1988 Fresh and Clean has been steam cleaning carpets and dry cleaning carpets in Toronto. Fresh and Clean’s green cleaning extends to upholstery cleaning and area rug cleaning also. In 2006 Fresh and Clean opened its York Region office extending it’s service into Vaughan, Woodbridge, Richmond Hill, Markham and Thornhill. We clean over 5,000 residences and commercial establishments per year. Fresh and Clean is a proud member firm of the (CFCRA) Canada Flooring Cleaning & Restoration Association, Wool Safe North America and the Wools of New Zealand. To keep our standing as an IICRC-certified firm, all our technicians must be formally educated in the cleaning and restoration fields, and are held up to a higher standard of professionalism and quality. We provide on going training of our employees to keep them abreast of the latest techniques and products available in the market place. Our cleaning solutions are certified by the Carpet and Rug Institute.

BA House Cleaning has recently partnered with Cleaning for a Reason. Fighting cancer is difficult enough, but living with it is even tougher and that’s where Cleaning For A Reason steps in. As a nonprofit serving the entire United States and Canada, they partner with maid services to offer professional house cleanings to help women undergoing treatment for cancer, any type of cancer. To date, they have helped more than 12,000 women with cancer with more than $3.2 million in donated cleanings, and partnered with over 1000 maid services. Please click on the logo to the right to check out their website for more information regarding this wonderful foundation.
BA House Cleaning was established in 2003 and since then we have built strong customer base and name recognition in the cleaning industry. We have been providing distinguished and wide range of cleaning services for our valued customers. We have well trained workers that are bonded for all maid services, office cleaning, and carpet cleaning services. Our specialist cleaning tasks are carried out throughout the area and recognized for best quality and standards by well-trained operatives to deliver sustainable cleaning services. We achieve this by paying attention to detail and efficiently managing every project from start to finish.
Since 2003, we have established close relationship with clients, the highest standard of services and competitive rates help us grow quickly. As a result, a large part of our business comes from repeat customers and referrals. We have expanded our cleaning service list and now we offer a range of cleaning services such as House Cleaning, Move in / Move out Cleaning, Carpet Cleaning, Pressure washing, Gutter Cleaning, Window Cleaning, Furniture Cleaning and Rug Cleaning.
Our guarantee is part of our commitment to our customers. We want our customers to be satisfied with the standard of cleaning we perform, and we welcome your comments to help us increase customer’s satisfaction. We provide all cleaning products and equipment necessary to complete every house cleaning and office cleaning job.
